
---

### **`.gitignore` File for Django + Redis + Python Projects**
```gitignore
# Byte-compiled / optimized / DLL files
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# Virtual environment
env/
venv/

# Django / Python-specific
*.sqlite3
db.sqlite3
*.log

# Environment variables & credentials
.env
config/settings_local.py

# Redis data
dump.rdb
appendonly.aof

# Ignore compiled Python files
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.pyc

# Ignore system-specific files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
